    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not the same. i look at the door or the couch and i expect to see him there, and then it hits me all over again. i'm just so tired of the cycle of loving something and then having it ripped away. it feels like i'm just waiting for the next bad thing to happen. what's even the point of trying to get better if it just hurts this much?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
